show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/VULFwp
show.description: When carefree Aarav Malhotra’s impulsive marriage to the strong-willed Anaya spirals into a battle of love, pride, and destiny, he must rise from an unlikely husband to the man fate has chosen him to be. Watch now!
